---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionIntro from '../components/SectionIntro.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Our Transition Team | North Texas Property Transition Services" description="Experienced North Texas professionals providing coordinated cleanout and property transition guidance for families navigating inherited and senior home transitions." pathname="/about">
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <SectionIntro eyebrow="About" title="About Our Transition Team" subtitle="Experienced North Texas professionals providing coordinated cleanout and property transition guidance for families navigating inherited and senior home transitions." />
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="info-card"><h3>A Coordinated Approach Was Missing</h3><p>Families often get pulled in several directions at once — cleanout, repairs, sale planning, and emotional decisions — without one clear process tying it all together.</p></div>
        <div class="info-card"><h3>Professional Cleanout &amp; Remediation Expertise</h3><p>Our process is built for situations where respectful cleanout, hoarding remediation, and practical property readiness all matter.</p></div>
        <div class="info-card"><h3>Property Transition &amp; Sale Guidance</h3><p>We help families evaluate whether to sell as-is, prepare selectively, or take a more involved route depending on the situation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="container split-grid">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Experience &amp; trust</div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Families need calm guidance, structure, and professionalism during a stressful season. That means thoughtful communication, practical recommendations, and a process designed to reduce confusion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Philosophy</div>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Cleanout and property strategy should be aligned from day one</li>
          <li>Decisions should be thoughtful, not reactive</li>
          <li>Families deserve transparency and professionalism</li>
          <li>Every situation requires a tailored approach</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTASection title="Families deserve a process that feels steady, not chaotic." body="North Texas Property Transition Services exists to bring calm structure to inherited home and senior transition decisions when the property itself is part of the stress." />
</BaseLayout>
